          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Processing_UtilityCompaniesListToProcess",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve a list of utility companies that can be processed for a given billing period. It is intended to populate a dropdown list with utility companies that meet specific criteria, ensuring that only those companies with unprocessed accounts for the specified billing period are included."
        }
      ]
    },
